{
  "stem": "24466.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] When that happens-- actually, I would like to go back a little bit.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remember it quite rightly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I was on the border with the Russia, in that little town, Korzec--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That is on the beginning of the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I notice that the army, the Russian army, and especially the one what were in the big trucks, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there have been colossal posters were showing from one side, we know-- and that was a known fact-- that Russia was with Germany, a written-- have got a written [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mentioned that to you before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] between Ribbentrop and that Molotov.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when I showed the trucks, the big trucks that were some big posters-- were SS, German, with their [NON-ENGLISH] [INAUDIBLE], blood's running from his mouth.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And a word here, keeping the standard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And with the cycle-- cycle and helmet, and this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I couldn't combine the two things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "On one side is written [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [NON-ENGLISH] between the two countries, between Russia and, and Germany.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And here, again, she poses like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I couldn't understand this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I came to-- so actually, I was thinking of this, that something is fishy in there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Something is-- will happen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the question, what you gave me now, is telling me that I was right.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That I was thinking about this, but I couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I couldn't believe it, really.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They came into Vilna through Klaipeda.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a port.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that happens on the 20-- no, when did they?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They invaded Lithuania on the 23rd, 23rd, of June.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they came in about two days later.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They came into Vilna already.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
